node.html: This project investigates the tendency of machine learning models to overfit when applied to medical datasets using a detailed examination of various machine learning models, emphasizing the conditions that lead to overfitting and evaluating methods to mitigate this issue.
A Go-based jump proxy that adds an extra layer of encryption to TCP services, enhancing their security against vulnerabilities.
Developed a TCP service fingerprinting tool that performs SYN scans and identifies services on open ports for network security purposes.
